# 2021 / Day 8: Seven Segment Search

## Puzzle

```elixir
puzzle =
  "./puzzles/day08.txt"
  |> Path.expand(__DIR__)
  |> File.read!()
  |> String.trim()
  |> String.split("\n")
  |> Enum.map(fn line ->
    [indices, output] = String.split(line, " | ")

    indices =
      indices
      |> String.split(" ")
      |> Enum.map(fn s ->
        s |> String.graphemes() |> Enum.sort() |> Enum.join()
      end)

    output =
      output
      |> String.split(" ")
      |> Enum.map(fn s ->
        s |> String.graphemes() |> Enum.sort() |> Enum.join()
      end)

    [indices, output]
  end)
```

